###############################################
nivo-slider-silverstripe-extension
SS2.4 tested
###############################################

20 July 2010
This is a full working version of nivo-slider for silverstripe.
All relevant Javascript options can be defined in the CMS


Maintainer Contact
-----------------------------------------------
Matt Clegg <cleggmatt (at) gmail (dot) com>
Nivo Slider is "The Most Awesome jQuery Image Slider". See http://nivo.dev7studios.com for more info.


Optional Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
DataobjectManager
SimpleTreeDropdownField


Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
Create a NivoSliderPage & customise Layout/NivoSliderPage.ss (it's all about the interface baby)


Known issues
-----------------------------------------------
CMS options are a bit mad


